Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,點和  1300
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.91,0:00:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是快速過莊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.87,0:00:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這樣的比賽中四次裏能和一次已經不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也是可以接受的吧
